Inkitanyaanyukot e Mika


1  Etii apa oltung'ani le nkop oo ndoinyo e Efraim oji enkarna enye Mika. 
2  Nejoki ninye ng'otonye, “Ore inapa pisai enkalifu nabo o iip nabo e nkosholai apa nikitooruoki iyie, naa ninche itedekishore, nidekisho too nkiyiaa aainei, ng'ura, aata nanu nena oshola; nanu apa oowa.” Nejo ng'otonye, “Metamayiana Olaitoriani enkayioni ai.” 
3  Nerrinyu ninye nena oshola apa enkalifu nabo o iip nabo aisho ng'otonye; nejo ng'otonye, “Kaiteng'el nanu kuna oshola aisho Olaitoriani aiwuang'ie te nkaina ai te nkaraki olayioni lai, pee eitayunyeki enkitanyaanyukoto e Nkai naguetuni o enkitanyaanyukoto nasholuni; ore naa taata kaarrinyoki nanu iyie.” 
4  Neaku ore apa pee errinyoki ninye ng'otonye nena pisai, neya ng'otonye mpisai iip are e nkosholai, neisho ninche ilkunono oopej enkosholai laa ninye oitobira enkitanyaanyukoto naguetuni o enkitanyaanyukoto nasholuni; nepiki apa enkaji e Mika. 
5  Neeta apa ltung'ani oji Mika enkaji oo nkaitin. Neitobiru ninye nkitanyaanyukot o enkila o lgoo oo lapolosak; neput olayioni obo loo layiok lenyena aitaa olapolosani lenye. 
6   Ore apa te nena olong'i nemeetae olaiguanani te Israel; keas apa pooki ng'ae enaba anaa esidai too nkonyek enyena makewan.


7  Etii apa oltung'ani le Betlehem ti atua Yuda, lo lmarei le Yuda, laa olawi apa ninye; neidurraki apa ninye ine. 
8  Nelo apa ilo tung'ani aing'uaa enkang e Betlehem te Yuda alo aton te wueji neidim anotie erishata; ore eidurrita ninye nelotu ina kop oo ldoinyo e Efraim enetii enkaji e Mika. 
9  Nejoki Mika ninye, “Kaji iyie ing'uaa?” Nejoki ninye, “Ara nanu Olawi le Betlehem ti atua Yuda, naa kalo amany ewueji naidim anotie erishata.” 
10  Nejoki Mika ninye, “Totona te nebo nanu pee iaku te nanu papa o lapolosani naaisho nanu mpisai tomon e nkosholai to lari o nkilani o endaa.” 
11  Nenyorraa ilo Lawi abik te nebo ilo tung'ani; netiu ilo barnoti te ninye anaa obo loo layiok lenyena. 
12  Neput Mika ilo Lawi, neaku ilo barnoti olapolosani lenye, netii apa ninye atua enkaji e Mika. 
13  Nejo apa Mika, “Ayiolo taata ajo kaaitopok Olaitoriani, amu aata Olawi aitaa olapolosani lai.”

